title: Warriors Most Dangerous Team In West?
description:
Jalen & Jacoby discuss the Warriors shutting down Jokic and Nuggets, Joel Embiid and Tyrese Maxey dominate Raptors, Jalen Brunson’s hot & spicy 41-piece on the Jazz, Marcus Smart wins DPOY, Kendrick Lamar announces new album, Jalen challenges Jacoby to recreate Meek Mill’s front flip, plus is tonight a must-win game for Grizzlies? All that and more!!!
